{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_07_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 譲れない好きの気持ち",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですね……うまく話せるか、分かりませんけど\nすみません……聞いて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… well… I'm not sure how to say it…\nI'm sorry… please listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ゆっくりで大丈夫だ\n話しているうちにまとまるかもしれないしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ take your time‚ it's okay.\nSometimes things come together as you talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n……今、気持ちがぐちゃぐちゃで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.\n…Right now‚ my feelings are all over the place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ファン感謝祭で着る衣装のことなんですけど……\n私は当然、二人時代の衣装を着るものだと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about the outfits for the fan festival…\nI thought I'd be supposed to wear the outfit from our duo days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛は、ずっと楽しみにしてたよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been looking forward to that‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.310839653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい……\nでも、でも……こころが……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…\nBut‚ but… Kokoro was like…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "四人で歌うことになったんだから、衣装だって\n四人体制のものとして新しくすべきだって言うんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we're going to sing as a quartet‚\nshe said the outfits should be new to reflect that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "私、ずっとこの曲に励まされてきました\nそれこそ、バンプロの練習生だった頃から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always been encouraged by this song.\nEver since I was a trainee at Van Prods…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それは私だけじゃありません\nこころも一緒なんです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not just me.\nIt's the same for Kokoro too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "辛い練習の後も、二人でこの曲を聴いて\nMVも、ライブのステージも観て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after tough practices‚ we listened to this song together…\nWatched the MV and the live performances…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5333301545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "何度オーディションに落ちても、諦めないで\n頑張ってこれたのは、この曲のおかげなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after failing auditions‚ we didn't give up‚\nall because of this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9487707038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "「どんなに辛いことがあっても立ち向かい続けよう」\nって……そうやって励まされてきた、特別な曲なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"No matter how tough things get‚ keep standing up\"\n…That's how we've been encouraged by this special song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5646844023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（歌詞の言葉を引用していたのは）\n（この曲の歌詞に励まされてきたからか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Quoting lyrics from the song…）\n（Because you've been encouraged by the lyrics of this song…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6453162824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、私は思い出の衣装で、先輩達と……\nこころと、ステージに立ちたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want to stand on stage with my memories‚ with my seniors…\nWith Kokoro‚ and sing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6333260855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、こころも同じ気持ちだって、私……勝手に……\nでも違ったから、喧嘩になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been getting my way that Kokoro feels the same way…\nBut it turned into an argument because we felt differently…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1666604361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほどな。愛もこころも、譲れないからこそ\n解決する気がしない……ということか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. Because neither you nor Kokoro could compromise…\nIt feels like there's no solution…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6342715463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "ずっとお互いリズノワが好きだったはずなのに\n大切な、思い出だったはずなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we both loved LizNoir so much…\nIt was such an important memory…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5666609448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、忘れちゃったの……こころの馬鹿……！\nうぅ……っ……私……私……っ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did we forget… Kokoro… You idiot…!\nUgh… I… I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0999983471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "愛……そうだな、一度気持ちを全部吐きだして\nそれからちゃんと考えよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi… yes‚ let it all out once…\nAnd then let's think about it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7666650137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8319029648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきは、泣いちゃってすみません\nちゃんと落ち着きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Earlier‚ I'm sorry I cried.\nI've calmed down now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2333316804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくていいよ\nそれだけ真剣なのは伝わってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it.\nYour seriousness came through clearly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4000034333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "はい……私、こころとこんなに真剣に喧嘩したの\n初めてで……余計に、どうしていいのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… it's just that I've never fought so seriously with Kokoro…\nI don't even know what to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1147895766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵はなんて言ってたんだ？\n当然その場にいたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did Rio-san and Aoi say?\nYou were there with them‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7333245596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……「まずは二人で話し合って\n自分達なりの答えを出してみなさい」と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… \"First‚ talk it out between the two of you…\nand come up with your own answers.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.766657893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "結局、お二人の気持ちは聞けなかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I couldn't hear their feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.5488739649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……それが二人の気持ちじゃないか？\n同じメンバーとして、意見を尊重したい、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Isn't that their way of expressing their feelings?\nAs fellow members‚ they want to respect each other's opinions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.5332577566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "なる、ほど……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.9713862578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、それぞれ自分で考えて、話し合って\n必要ならぶつかり合って、答えを出してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ each should think on their own‚ talk it out‚\nand if necessary‚ clash to find the answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.5333388013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それが莉央さんと葵なりの、四人体制になった\nLizNoirへの気持ちなんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how Rio-san and Aoi have approached\nthe quartet formation for LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.0999830884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "こころは……\nこころも、そう思ってるんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about Kokoro…?\nWould Kokoro feel the same way too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.1333164217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "私、こんなにこころが分からないのが初めてで\n考えが違うとは思わなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the first time I don't understand Kokoro so much…\nI didn't think our thoughts would differ…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.6042277096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "衣装のことで妥協しても、しなくても\n関係が壊れちゃうんじゃないか、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether we compromise on the outfits or not‚\nI'm afraid our relationship might break down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.533317439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "仲が良くても、ぶつかることはあるさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you get along well‚ you can still clash.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.4756400185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.4122219799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、最近だと、怜と遙子さん……\n芽衣とすずも、ぶつかっていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ recently‚ it was Rei and Haruko-san…\nMei and Suzu too‚ clashed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.3392034714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　ぜ、全然そんな風に見えません\nだって、凄く仲がいいままで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh!? No way… They didn't seem that way at all to me…\nThey've always been so close…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.4666548412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それは違うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.5398860848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_02-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "う、裏ではギスギス……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-huh‚ behind the scenes…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.2415640827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
