      "text": "ぶつかった結果、お互いが理解を深める\nそれで、より良いものが生まれたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By clashing‚ they understood each other better.\nThat's why something better was created",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.6333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
