      "text": "だから愛も、こころに向き合ってみたらどうだ\n一歩踏み出す勇気って怖いだろうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So why don't you try facing Kokoro head-on?\nI know It's scary to take that first step…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
